release 1:
internal commands:
- cd
- cd <dir>
- ls
- ls <dir>
- environ
- echo <cmd>
- help
- quit

release 2:
fork() and exec() all other statements.

release 3:
batch files as args.

release 4:
io redirection using < and >, eg:
app arg1 arg < inputfile > outputfile
this includes ls, environ, echo and help.

release 5:
support background execution using ampersand.

release 6:
change to prompt to show the current dir name.